381
00:19:01,079 --> 00:19:01,720
Mom

382
00:19:04,799 --> 00:19:05,359
Son

383
00:19:06,039 --> 00:19:07,799
I'll go to Hetian with you.

384
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:10,359
Mom

385
00:19:11,279 --> 00:19:12,640
I'll go find An Dong first.

386
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:13,799
See what's going on.

387
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:15,480
Then you can come over.

388
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,319
I've been through more than you.

389
00:19:17,799 --> 00:19:19,480
Maybe I can help if I go.

390
00:19:21,079 --> 00:19:21,759
But

391
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:23,799
