Mom

415
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,440
Don't worry.

416
00:20:31,119 --> 00:20:32,039
He definitely won't do

417
00:20:32,039 --> 00:20:33,480
anything to hurt himself.

418
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:45,279
I've already checked the guesthouses.

419
00:20:45,799 --> 00:20:47,000
He didn't take his phone or luggage.

420
00:20:47,039 --> 00:20:48,799
Is there anywhere else he usually goes?

421
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:51,799
I've looked everywhere I could.

422
00:20:52,279 --> 00:20:52,799
Ming Liang

423
00:20:53,319 --> 00:20:54,559
I have a bad feeling about this.

424
00:20:58,559 --> 00:20:59,880
Is there anywhere in Hetian

425
00:21:00,519 --> 00:21:02,039
