426
00:21:02,359 --> 00:21:03,480
An Dong always has you in his heart.

427
00:21:04,039 --> 00:21:04,920
If he really wants to do something,

428
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:06,039
he might go to that place.

429
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,240
An Dong, look!

430
00:21:16,559 --> 00:21:17,559
It's a Glossy Ibis.

431
00:21:18,279 --> 00:21:19,039
When I was little,

432
00:21:19,039 --> 00:21:20,759
