443
00:21:50,519 --> 00:21:51,599
Can I ask you something?

444
00:21:52,039 --> 00:21:53,559
If Ankaer learns from you,

445
00:21:53,799 --> 00:21:55,519
can he ever be like you?

446
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:00,799
You need someone to support you now.

447
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:02,519
I want to stand by your side.

448
00:22:03,119 --> 00:22:04,839
Everyone in our restaurant

449
00:22:05,039 --> 00:22:06,480
gives you their heart.

450
00:22:06,839 --> 00:22:08,440
We treat you with all our sincerity.

451
00:22:08,519 --> 00:22:09,640
That's how we all treat you.

452
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:11,039
Why do you treat us like this?

453
00:22:11,039 --> 00:22:12,440
What kind of person are you?

454
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:13,519
An Dong

455
00:22:14,240 --> 00:22:16,720
You don't understand what family means.

456
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:20,599
Winning people's hearts is the hardest.

457
00:22:21,400 --> 00:22:22,720
You won their hearts,

458
00:22:23,119 --> 00:22:25,240
