459
00:22:26,160 --> 00:22:27,079
Do you think by doing this

460
00:22:27,079 --> 00:22:28,519
they'll forgive you?

461
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:30,039
An Dong...

462
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:34,480
You brought yourself to this dead end.

463
00:22:43,079 --> 00:22:43,799
An Dong

464
00:22:46,759 --> 00:22:47,359
An Dong

465
00:22:48,480 --> 00:22:49,559
What are you doing, An Dong?

466
00:22:50,039 --> 00:22:50,720
Where are you going?

467
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:51,799
Leave me alone.

468
00:22:52,559 --> 00:22:53,400
Let me die.

469
00:22:53,400 --> 00:22:54,000
An Dong

470
00:22:54,559 --> 00:22:55,640
An Dong

471
00:22:57,480 --> 00:22:57,880
Let go.

