00:22:58,920 --> 00:22:59,359
Let go.

473
00:22:59,359 --> 00:23:00,000
An Dong

474
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:01,200
Does dying solve anything?

475
00:23:01,759 --> 00:23:02,799
Does dying solve anything?

476
00:23:03,039 --> 00:23:05,799
Me living just makes you all suffer more.

477
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:06,960
Let me die.

478
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:08,079
If you die like this,

479
00:23:08,079 --> 00:23:09,519
we'll feel guilty for the rest of our lives.

480
00:23:09,519 --> 00:23:10,480
I don't deserve it.

481
00:23:10,599 --> 00:23:12,200
I don't deserve your guilt.

482
00:23:12,519 --> 00:23:13,480
Let me die.

483
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:15,079
Let me die.

484
00:23:15,119 --> 00:23:15,559
An Dong

485
00:23:16,279 --> 00:23:17,279
Are you even a man?

486
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:18,680
You want our whole family

487
00:23:19,279 --> 00:23:21,079
to spend the rest of our lives paying your debts?

488
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,440
Who made you do this?

489
00:23:44,519 --> 00:23:46,079
Why do you want to die?

490
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,799
Why are you doing this?

491
00:23:47,799 --> 00:23:48,799
What gives you the right?

492
00:23:48,839 --> 00:23:50,599
Can you live with yourself after this?

493
00:23:50,599 --> 00:23:52,480
Can you face the people around you?

494
00:23:53,799 --> 00:23:55,559
An Dong, look at me.

495
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:56,880
Look at me.

496
00:23:57,920 --> 00:23:59,759
