499
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:06,680
You're healthy and well.

500
00:24:06,799 --> 00:24:09,079
Why do you want to take this step?

501
00:24:09,119 --> 00:24:09,880
Aisha

502
00:24:11,599 --> 00:24:12,359
I don't deserve it.

503
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:15,680
I don't deserve your worry.

504
00:24:15,880 --> 00:24:16,960
I really don't deserve it.

505
00:24:17,480 --> 00:24:18,240
An Dong

506
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,039
I don't deserve it.

507
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:20,480
Let me tell you something.

508
00:24:21,039 --> 00:24:22,240
Once you join Hong Shiliu,

509
00:24:23,319 --> 00:24:25,039
