519
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:47,160
What are you saying? I can't fix it.

520
00:24:48,279 --> 00:24:50,839
Didn't you ask Hatiman for a million?

521
00:24:56,079 --> 00:24:56,799
A million.

522
00:24:58,359 --> 00:24:59,279
