525
00:25:11,279 --> 00:25:12,000
Okay.

526
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:13,960
As long as nothing happened to him.

527
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:15,079
Otherwise, he'd get off too easy.

528
00:25:15,599 --> 00:25:16,480
How's everything at the restaurant?

529
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:18,319
