536
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:29,680
So I came as soon as I had time off.

537
00:25:29,960 --> 00:25:30,759
Thanks, brother.

538
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:32,119
No need to thank me.

539
00:25:32,279 --> 00:25:33,079
I can't really help much.

540
00:25:33,079 --> 00:25:34,079
I'm just here for a free meal.

541
00:25:34,359 --> 00:25:34,759
By the way—

542
00:25:34,759 --> 00:25:35,839
