908
00:43:10,679 --> 00:43:12,679
I'll help shield you

909
00:43:12,920 --> 00:43:14,079
from outside waves.

910
00:43:16,679 --> 00:43:17,800
You really are

911
00:43:18,599 --> 00:43:21,159
more proactive than the person involved.

912
00:43:21,280 --> 00:43:22,639
When he comes back from Hetian,

913
00:43:22,639 --> 00:43:23,360
